acknowledgement.excerpt: Thank [@fzyzcjy](https://github.com/fzyzcjy) for your help in this project.

description.excerpt:
A Keras implementation of MobileNetV3 and Lite R-ASPP Semantic Segmentation (Under Development). 
According to the paper: Searching for MobileNetV3

invocation.excerpt: The config/config.json file provide a config for training.

Run command below to train the model: 
python train_cls.py
